<div id="pf4" class="pf w4 hf" data-page-no="4"><div class="pc pc4 w4 hf"><img class="bi x0 y0 w5 h10" alt="" src="bg4.png"/><div class="t m79 xb h11 y60 ff2 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Meet the Principal Contributor of </div><div class="t m7a x14 h11 y61 ff2 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This Quarter&apos;s Lessons </div><div class="t m7b x21 h12 y62 ff5 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Rosalie Haffner Lee trains and supervises Bible instructors in the Carolina </div><div class="t m2f x1e h12 y63 ff5 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Conference. Working as a Bible instructor and a pastor&apos;s wife has been the focus </div><div class="t m7c x1e h12 y64 ff5 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of her career. </div><div class="t m7d x21 h12 y65 ff5 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Mrs. Lee received her Bachelor of Arts degree from Union College, and </div><div class="t m7e x1e h12 y66 ff5 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">served as Bible instructor in California, Nebraska, and Michigan. She was an in-</div><div class="t m7f x1e h12 y67 ff5 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">structor for the North American Division Evangelism Institute in Illinois before </div><div class="t m80 x1e h12 y68 ff5 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">accepting the position in the Carolina Conference. </div><div class="t m81 x21 h12 y69 ff5 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Mrs. Lee has written a previous set of Sabbath School lessons, </div><div class="t m82 x22 h13 y6a ff8 fsc fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Songs of Ex-</div><div class="t m83 x1e h13 y6b ff8 fsc fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">perience, </div><div class="t m84 x23 h12 y6c ff5 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">on the Psalms, and authored a book entitled </div><div class="t m85 x24 h13 y6d ff8 fsc fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Let Me Tell You About My </div><div class="t m86 x13 h13 y6e ff8 fsc fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God. </div><div class="t m87 x3 h12 y6f ff5 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In addition she has written for several Adventist publications. </div><div class="t m88 x21 h12 y70 ff5 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Cooking, writing, and bird-watching occupy Mrs. Lee&apos;s leisure moments. Her </div><div class="t m89 x1e h12 y71 ff5 fsb fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">husband, Kenneth, is a retired pastor. </div><div class="t m8a x12 h14 y72 ff5 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Check at your local Adventist Book Center </div><div class="t m8b x12 h14 y73 ff5 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for the companion book to the Sabbath </div><div class="t m8c x12 h14 y74 ff5 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">School Lessons. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
